    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01473.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">Sheldon House <lb/>Ocean Grove <choice>
                            <abbr>N.J.</abbr>
                            <expan>New Jersey</expan>
                        </choice></name>
                    <date when="1883-09-21" rend="right">Sept 21<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="superscript">st</hi></hi></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Walt:</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I am down here for a week or two, under the direction of my Dr, taking hot sea baths.
                Came here last Monday, a pleasant place with plenty of sea &amp; sea air. I feel well
                &amp; walk some days 8 or 10 miles, <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low"
                    resp="#nnk">but</unclear> there are certain symptoms that the Dr thinks hot baths
                will <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01473.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
                <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.01473.003_large.jpg" type="recto"/>remove. Now
                mainly what I write for is this, to ask you to come up &amp; be my guest for a week.
                I <choice>
                    <orig>cant</orig>
                    <reg>can't</reg>
                </choice> come to you very well, but <choice>
                    <orig>cant</orig>
                    <reg>can't</reg>
                </choice> you come to me? This is a large comfortable House with few guests,
                near the beach &amp; you would feel at home here. <choice><orig>Cant</orig><reg>Can't</reg></choice> you come? Come to-morrow
                (Saturday) &amp; send me a dispatch what train. We can have the Atlantic Ocean all
                to ourselves, &amp; maybe these hot sea baths at the hotel are the thing for you.
                Do come.</p>

            <closer>
                <salute rend="middle">With love</salute>
                <signed rend="right">J Burroughs</signed>
            </closer>
